I.PR_COD, I.CALCUL, I.REG_PAID, '№' || P.NUM_DOC || ' от ' || P.DATE_DOC AS PAYORDER FROM DBF_TPO_ITP I, DBF_TPO_PLT P WHERE NVL(P.VIDNAC,I.COD_MAINPL) = I.COD_MAINPL AND P.NUM_TPO=I.NUM_TPO");
